asis on accurate diagnosis. <em>Am J Surg</em> 1968;115(1):89–96.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/0002-9610(68)90134-7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5634681/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Vascular+compression+of+the+duodenum%3A+emphasis+on+accurate+diagnosis&amp;author=AR+Mansberger&amp;author=JB+Hearn&amp;author=RM+Byers&amp;author=N+Fleisig&amp;author=RW+Buxton&amp;publication_year=1968&amp;journal=Am+J+Surg&amp;pages=89-96&amp;doi=10.1016%2F0002-9610%2868%2990134-7&amp;pmid=5634681">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">22.</div><div id="r22" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Merrett ND, Wilson RB, Cosman P, Biankin AV. Superior mesenteric artery syndrome: diagnosisand treatment strategies. <em>J Gastrointest Surg</em> 2009;13(2):287–292.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11605-008-0695-4">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18810558/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Superior+mesenteric+artery+syndrome%3A+diagnosisand+treatment+strategies&amp;author=ND+Merrett&amp;author=RB+Wilson&amp;author=P+Cosman&amp;author=AV+Biankin&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=J+Gastrointest+Surg&amp;pages=287-292&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs11605-008-0695-4&amp;pmid=18810558">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">23.</div><div id="r23" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Welsch T, Büchler MW, Kienle P. Recalling superior mesenteric artery syndrome. <em>Dig Surg</em> 2007; 24(3):149–156