ad Al-Kutoubi</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Mohamad Hamady</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Mohamad Khalifeh</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ali Hallal</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Hamzeh M. Halawani</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Joelle Wazen</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ali A. Haydar</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">3 January 2017 | CardioVascular and Interventional Radiology, Vol. 40, No. 5</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00270-016-1560-6">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.rhum.2016.09.005"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rhum.2016.09.005">Le syndrome nutcracker : une cause rare de douleurs lombaires gauches mais aussi de souffrances pelviennes inexpliquées</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Jean-Marie Berthelot</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Frédéric Douane</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Yves Maugars</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Eric Frampas</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2017Mar1 | Revue du Rhumatisme, Vol. 84, No. 2</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rhum.2016.09.005">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/s00261-016-0779-7"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00261-016-0779-7">Caught in a “nutcracker”</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height">